Write mode types if table exists.

Namespace: Google.Cloud.Asset.V1
Assembly: Google.Cloud.Asset.V1.dll
Syntax
public enum WriteMode

Fields

Name Description
Abort

Abort the export when table or partition exists.
Overwrite

Overwrite the table when table exists. When partitioned, overwrite the existing partition.
Unspecified

Unspecified write mode. We expect one of the following valid modes must be specified when table or partition exists.
